title: Football Friday In KELOLAND
text:
October 2, 2015, 4:11 AM SIOUX FALLS, SD - 
It's Friday in KELOLAND and that means it is time for high school football. 
The matchup between 11AAA #3 O'Gorman at 11AA #3 Yankton will be our livestream game of the week. Kickoff is at 7 p.m. 
The KELOLAND Sports team will bring you highlights from 10 games across South Dakota following the 10 p.m. news. 11AA #2 Brookings @ 11AAA #1 Roosevelt 11AAA Rapid City Central @ 11AAA #4 Brandon Valley 11AAA #3 O'Gorman @ 11AA #3 Yankton 11AA Douglas @ 11A #2 St. Thomas More 11A #3 Sioux Falls Christian @ 11A #1 Madison 11A #4 West Central @ 11A #5 Lennox 11A Vermillion @ 11A Tea Area 9AA #2 Wolsey-Wessington @ 9B Sunshine Bible Academy 9AA Gregory @ 9AA #1 Woonsocket/Wessington Springs/Sanborn Central 9AA Mt. Vernon/Plankinton @ 9A #1 Canistota 
Tune into the KELOLAND SportsZone at 10:30 p.m. for the highlights. 
We want to see what you see at the games. Share your pictures and videos with us by emailing ushare@keloland.com ; submitting a photo using the KELOLAND News App ; upload it to the uShare Photo Gallery ; or use #kelosports when you post on Facebook, Twitter or Instagram. Sports Resources
